com.diffplug.gradle.spotless

Class LazyForwardingEquality<T extends Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diffplug.gradle.spotless.LazyForwardingEquality<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FormatterStep.Strict

    public abstract class LazyForwardingEquality<T extends Serializable>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Implements equality, hashcode, and serialization entirely in terms of a lazily-computed key. The key's serialized form is used to implement equals() and hashCode(), so you don't have to.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

protected abstract T calculateKey()
